                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>For texts of messages from President Truman to Governors-General Mohammed Ali
                    Jinnah and Lord Louis Mountbatten on the occasion of the coming into being of
                    the new Dominions of Pakistan and India on August 15, see Department of State
                        <hi rend="italic">Bulletin</hi>, August 24, 1947, page 396.</p>
            </div>
